 &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Heart of Light&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Reduces magic damage taken by 10% and physical damage taken by 5% for self and party members in a 30y radius around you for 15 seconds. 90 second cooldown.&lt;/td&gt;
