&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Low Blow&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Role action. Stuns a target for five seconds. Enemies that get stunned repeatedly will develop stun immunity. 25s cooldown.&lt;/td&gt;
